## ğŸŒˆ Crear Patrones de Colores

```elixir
colores = ["rojo", "azul", "verde", "amarillo", "morado"]

html_colores =
  Enum.map(colores, fn color ->
    """
    <div style="background-color: #{color}; padding: 20px; margin: 5px; border-radius: 10px; color: white; font-weight: bold;">
      #{String.upcase(color)}
    </div>
    """
  end)
  |> Enum.join("")

Kino.Markdown.new(html_colores)
```

